metadata.name: Hermemetism enriched with death
metadata.description:
A 1/1 page for a Grimemeire enriched with death series. There is a Hermetic Law 3.0 'Meme is art and Art is Meme, Meme is Life and Life is Meme, Meme is Internet and Internet is Meme. Who controls the memes, controls the Universe.' 
This new memethological creatures would enrich the collection.
